content: Place in Singapore **Bukit Batok Central** is a subzone of [Bukit Batok](/wiki/Bukit_Batok). It is bounded by Bukit Batok West Avenue 6/3, Central, East Avenue 3/6. ## Housing estates RoadsEstate nameBlocksQuantityNoteBukit Batok Central620-64410 ## Politics It is part of the Bukit Batok constituency since 2015. Along with their neighbouring Bukit Batok East, Yuhua and Hong Kah (Jurong East/West), it was one of the founding constituencies for Jurong GRC in 2001. ## Neighbouring Areas This [Singapore](/wiki/Singapore) location article is a stub.
